<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>決済エラー - gibtee</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Hiragino Sans', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 90%;
      width: 500px;
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .error-icon {
      color: #E74C3C;
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #E74C3C;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .error-message {
      background: #FADBD8;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #C0392B;
    }
    .close-button {
      background-color: #3498DB;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .close-button:hover {
      background-color: #2980B9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
    <h1>決済処理中にエラーが発生しました</h1>
    <div class="error-message">
      <%= message %>
    </div>
    <p>LINEアプリに戻り、もう一度お試しいただくか、別の支払い方法をお選びください。</p>
    <button class="close-button" onclick="window.close()">ブラウザを閉じる</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
